# MyFleetDotBuild
![some alt text](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

**MyFleetDotBuild** is a web-based application designed to help car enthusiasts and collectors manage their personal vehicle collections. With features like detailed car and rim records, image uploads, and a user-friendly interface, organizing your fleet has never been easier.

## Features
+ **Add & Edit Vehicles** Input comprehensive details about each car, including make, model, year, and more.

+ **Read & Delete Vehicles** You can also view and delete each vehicle as the user of the page.

+ **Rim Management** Associate custom rims with vehicles, complete with brand and specifications.

+ **Image Uploads** Upload and display images for both cars and rims to visualize your collection.

+ **Responsive Design** Enjoy a sleek, dark-themed interface optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.

+ **Secure Authentication** Protect your data with secure user login and management.

## Usage

+ **Dashboard**: View an overview of your car collection.

+ **Add Car**: Navigate to the "Add Car" section to input new vehicle details.

+ **Edit Car**: Click on a car entry to update its information or associated rims.

+ **Add Rim**: Manage your rim inventory and link them to specific vehicles.â€‹

## Software Requirements

+ Django 3.2+
